                {\"text\":\"§lSecrets of the Hidden Room
\"},
                {\"text\":\"~~~~~~~~~
\"},
                {\"text\":\"Few who venture into the Ancient Factory uncover its hidden chamber, yet its secrets remain locked behind clever mechanisms. \"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"The Ancients, ever wary of intruders, devised a test for those who sought their greatest treasures. To unlock the chamber, one must find and flick two levers within the factory.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"Only then can the final step be completed: pressing the button to the left of the Harbinger's chamber. It is said that the mechanism activates in perfect harmony, revealing the treasures hidden behind cold, unyielding walls.\"}
              ]",
              "[
                {\"text\":\"But beware—the Harbinger stirs when its domain is disturbed. Complete the puzzle quickly, or risk awakening the factory's guardian before you are prepared.\"}
              ]"
            ],
            title:Journal,
            author:CraisinLord,
            display:{Lore:["Bam"]}
            }

